These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, metal
1. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of metal##1
2. the fan of metal is not to the right of the fan of metal##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2  |
| Music-Genre   | metal | folk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: spy, sports
1. the person watching spy movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching spy movies is not to the left of the person watching sports movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | spy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-3::.
2 different pets are kept: rat, chinchilla
1. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##5
2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
3. the owner of the rat is not to the right of the owner of the rat##8

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |    2     |
| Pet   | rat | chinchilla |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-4::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, skateboard
1. the person driving the quad-bike is not to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##8
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2   |
| Transport   | quad-bike | skateboard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-8-5::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, baking
1. the person who's hobby is baking is not to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##8
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |   2    |
| Hobby   | baking | fishing |

 #################################

 
